title.narrative: COMPONENT 1: DELIVERY OF HEALTH SERVICES

description.narrative: Component 1: Improved delivery of essential health services in the former states of Upper Nile and Jonglei, which contributes to Cross-Sectoral - Social And Behaviour Change, Health And Development In Early Childhood And Adolescence, Immunization Services As Part Of Primary Health Care, Operations Support To Programme Delivery, Strengthening Primary Health Care And High-Impact Health Interventions. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Community Engagement, Social And Behaviour Change, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building, Systems Strengthening To Leave No One Behind. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: New Element
